  "title": "CARPENTER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description / Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Must be able to read drawing</li><li>Good understanding of work process</li><li>Must be able to operable carpentry machine and equipment </li><li>Carry out construction carpentry works including formwork, fixing, and installation </li><li> Install doors, frames, partitions, and other wooden structures</li><li> Repair and maintain existing carpentry structures at construction sites</li><li> Follow safety regulations and site supervisor instructions</li><li> Ensure work quality meets project and site requirements</li></ul><ul><li><strong>Requirements:</strong></li><li> Minimum <strong>5 years of relevant experience</strong> as a construction carpenter</li><li> Experience working on construction sites</li><li>Knowledge of carpentry tools, equipment, and materials</li><li> Able to work independently and as part of a team</li></ul>",
